sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User (Browser)
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Edge
    participant UI as Streamlit UI<br/>8501/TCP HTTP
    participant Backend as FastAPI Backend<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Ollama as Ollama LLM<br/>11434/TCP HTTP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant BentoML as BentoML llm-optimizer<br/>(in-process)
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MC as Model Catalog API<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User, K8s: Flow 1: End-to-End Recommendation

    User->>Router: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)
    Router->>UI: HTTP/8501 (TLS terminated)
    UI->>Backend: POST /api/v1/extract<br/>HTTP/8000 (internal)
    Backend->>Ollama: POST /api/chat<br/>HTTP/11434 (no auth)
    Ollama-->>Backend: Structured DeploymentIntent
    Backend-->>UI: Extracted intent JSON

    UI->>Backend: POST /api/v1/ranked-recommend-from-spec<br/>HTTP/8000 (internal)
    Backend->>PG: SQL query (benchmark lookup)<br/>TCP/5432 (password auth)
    PG-->>Backend: Benchmark results
    Backend->>HF: GET model config<br/>HTTPS/443 (Bearer Token optional)
    HF-->>Backend: Model architecture metadata
    Backend->>BentoML: Roofline estimation<br/>(in-process, no network)
    BentoML-->>Backend: Performance estimates
    Backend-->>UI: 5 ranked recommendation lists

    UI->>Backend: POST /api/v1/deploy-to-cluster<br/>HTTP/8000 (internal)
    Backend->>Backend: Jinja2 template rendering<br/>(KServe InferenceService YAML)
    Backend->>K8s: kubectl apply InferenceService<br/>HTTPS/6443 (SA token)
    K8s-->>Backend: Deployment status
    Backend-->>UI: Deployment confirmation
    UI-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: HTTPS response

    Note over Backend, MC: Flow 2: Model Catalog Sync (RHOAI Mode)

    Backend->>MC: GET /api/model_catalog/v1alpha1/...<br/>HTTPS/8443 (SA token, service-ca TLS)
    MC-->>Backend: Model & benchmark data
    Backend->>PG: INSERT benchmarks<br/>TCP/5432 (password auth)
    PG-->>Backend: Insert confirmation

    Note over User, HF: Flow 3: Capacity Planning

    User->>Router: HTTPS/443
    Router->>Backend: POST /api/v1/model-info<br/>HTTP/8000
    Backend->>HF: GET model config<br/>HTTPS/443 (Bearer Token optional)
    HF-->>Backend: Model config (params, layers)
    Backend->>HF: GET safetensors metadata<br/>HTTPS/443 (Bearer Token optional)
    HF-->>Backend: Safetensors index
    Backend-->>Router: GPU memory requirements
    Router-->>User: Capacity analysis
